Edge Cases Identified
Edge Case	Why It Matters
No due date	Should not crash, score based on priority only
Due exactly today	Hits the == 0 condition specifically
URGENT + DONE combined	60 - 50 = 10, counterintuitive result
Tag Blocker (capital B)	Gets no boost — silent bug without test
Updated 23 hours ago	Still gets +5 — calendar days not hours
Unknown priority value	.get() returns 0 — should this error?

